pkg/
**/pkg/
*.wasm

# ── SpacetimeDB generated client bindings ─────────────
# Derived from the schema — regenerate with `spacetime generate`. Ignored on purpose
# (they change every schema edit; `spacetime dev` regenerates them automatically).
frontend/src/module_bindings/
**/module_bindings/

